{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-074__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-074", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-074__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 74.1", "sort_key": "074.001", "text_original": "民不畏死，奈何以死懼之？若使民常畏死，而為奇者，吾得執而殺之，孰敢？", "text_normalized": "民不畏死，奈何以死懼之？若使民常畏死，而為奇者，吾得執而殺之，孰敢？", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-074__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-074", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-074__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 74.2", "sort_key": "074.002", "text_original": "常有司殺者殺，夫代司殺者殺，是謂代大匠斲。夫代大匠斲者，希有不傷其手矣。", "text_normalized": "常有司殺者殺，夫代司殺者殺，是謂代大匠斲。夫代大匠斲者，希有不傷其手矣。", "notes": ""}
